Package io.github.atreia108.vega.core

Class InteractionClassProfile

java.lang.Object
io.github.atreia108.vega.core.InteractionClassProfile
public final class InteractionClassProfile extends Object

Internal representation of an HLA interaction class. The profile of an interaction class is used for mapping data converters and parameter handles of the class; typically necessary when creating an interaction of the class from an ECS entity.

Like the ObjectClassProfile, it is generated at runtime from the simulation project file and subsequently stored in the ProjectRegistry.

Since:
1.0.0
Author:
Hridyanshu Aatreya
